!rootyarfaroooo 🦭🌳

🌳 There are already a ton of Roos that hold Seals and visa versa so, it makes perfect sense to make the cross-pollination we've been working on official.

🌳 SS is a marketing & branding goldmine that will help RT in multiple areas that we haven't spent too much time on.

🌳 SS community is full of hungry (and VETERAN) NFTers who want to build in Web3. Bringing them into our ecosystem is great for our expansion.

🌳 Sappy Seals have one of the strongest communities in the NFT realm, next to the Troop of course...and we know joining our two powerhouses of communities will result in greatness for all parties involved.
